## Proprietary Components Notice

The following modules contain stubbed implementations. The full production
logic is proprietary to Liminal Space and is not included in this repository:

- `src/lib/semiotic/compiler.ts` — Semiotic compiler (experience → artifact)
- `src/lib/council/pattern-detection.ts` — Archetype pattern analysis
- `src/lib/archetypes/shadow-dialogue.ts` — Shadow-archetype routing

The EverMemOS integration layer (`src/lib/evermemos/`) and all other code
in this repository is covered by the MIT License above.

Type definitions (`src/lib/semiotic/types.ts`, `src/types/`) are included
under MIT to demonstrate the domain model architecture.
